Rap mega star Nicki Minaj and hubby Kenneth Petty are expecting their first bundle of joy together. Last month Nicki confirmed that she married Kenneth, who is her childhood sweetheart, and now the pair are well on their way to becoming parents. Taking to her Instagram account, the star posted several pictures of her baby bump. She said in one of the captions that she was grateful. "Love. Marriage. Baby carriage. Overflowing with gratitude. Thank you for all your well wishes," the 37-year-old star announced to her more than 100 million Instagram followers. SEE POST BELOW: Love. Marriage. Baby carriage. Overflowing with excitement & gratitude. Thank you all for the well wishes. ?? A post shared by  Barbie (@nickiminaj) on Jul 20, 2020 at 8:08am PDT 